{"tid":1847421,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"深水埗區議員助理檢查橫額　遭警以涉刑毁拘捕","createTime":"2020-01-28T05:02:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T06:04:51.000Z","uid":53379,"like":7,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"9c087fd93048f4e74ee5e75a3d4bac74157dec4c","tid":1847421,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:02:56.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">深水埗區議員助理檢查橫額 遭警以涉刑毁拘捕 </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200128/s00001/275d522efbcd54e3e60091ab543227ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200128%2Fs00001%2F275d522efbcd54e3e60091ab543227ae.jpg&h=f2982a16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖4之1 - 劉家衡在facebook發布圖片，稱其助理欲檢查橫額有否被損毁時，遭便衣警以涉嫌刑事毁壞拘捕。（劉家衡facebook圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200128/s00001/275c4e4dd9e42a58b535a2e584d2b85d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200128%2Fs00001%2F275c4e4dd9e42a58b535a2e584d2b85d.jpg&h=9aed0697&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖4之2 - 劉家衡指稱警方不滿其合法橫額的標語，擅自以垃圾膠袋套上橫額。（劉家衡facebook圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200128/s00001/275cc544ce11e9c14ede415f31cd7661.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200128%2Fs00001%2F275cc544ce11e9c14ede415f31cd7661.jpg&h=613ab650&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖4之3 - 劉家衡指稱警方不滿其合法橫額的標語，擅自以垃圾膠袋套上橫額。（劉家衡facebook圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200128/s00001/275bd824b104a98cb2afe5c60e3987b0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200128%2Fs00001%2F275bd824b104a98cb2afe5c60e3987b0.jpg&h=91b18ccb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖4之4 - 劉家衡的助理陳樂行拉開膠袋欲檢查橫額有否被損毁時，遭便衣警以涉嫌刑事毁壞拘捕。（劉家衡facebook圖片）<br />\n<br />\n今日（28日）中午近12時，深水埗南昌區區議員劉家衡一名助理於長沙灣道與南昌街交界檢查其議辦的橫額期間，被警方以涉嫌刑事毁壞拘捕。本報正就事件向警方查詢。<br />\n<br />\n劉家衡在facebook表示，他們早前於該合法位置掛上寫有「願香港制警惡除警姦」的橫額，警方曾要求移除橫額，並於未有通知下以垃圾膠袋套上橫額，他與助理陳樂行到場時，發現大批便衣警員看守垃圾膠袋，陳樂行上前拉開膠袋欲檢查橫額有否被損毁時，即遭便衣警以刑事毁壞垃圾膠袋將其拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200128/s00001/1580184676700/%e6%b7%b1%e6%b0%b4%e5%9f%97%e5%8d%80%e8%ad%b0%e5%93%a1%e5%8a%a9%e7%90%86%e6%aa%a2%e6%9f%a5%e6%a9%ab%e9%a1%8d-%e9%81%ad%e8%ad%a6%e4%bb%a5%e6%b6%89%e5%88%91%e6%af%81%e6%8b%98%e6%8d%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200128%2Fs00001%2F1580184676700%2F%25e6%25b7%25b1%25e6%25b0%25b4%25e5%259f%2597%25e5%258d%2580%25e8%25ad%25b0%25e5%2593%25a1%25e5%258a%25a9%25e7%2590%2586%25e6%25aa%25a2%25e6%259f%25a5%25e6%25a9%25ab%25e9%25a1%258d-%25e9%2581%25ad%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e4%25bb%25a5%25e6%25b6%2589%25e5%2588%2591%25e6%25af%2581%25e6%258b%2598%25e6%258d%2595&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtb8jT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=4caba4fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200128%2Fs00001%2F1580184676700%2F%25e6%25b7%25b1%25e6%25b0%25b4%25e5%259f%2597%25e5%258d%2580%25e8%25ad%25b0%25e5%2593%25a1%25e5%258a%25a9%25e7%2590%2586%25e6%25aa%25a2%25e6%259f%25a5%25e6%25a9%25ab%25e9%25a1%258d-%25e9%2581%25ad%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e4%25bb%25a5%25e6%25b6%2589%25e5%2588%2591%25e6%25af%2581%25e6%258b%2598%25e6%258d%2595&h=26a3aa53\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200128/s00001/1580184676700/%e6%b7%b1%e6%b0%b4%e5%9f%97%e5%8d%80%e8%ad%b0%e5%93%a1%e5%8a%a9%e7%90%86%e6%aa%a2%e6%9f%a5%e6%a9%ab%e9%a1%8d-%e9%81%ad%e8%ad%a6%e4%bb%a5%e6%b6%89%e5%88%91%e6%af%81%e6%8b%98%e6%8d%95</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"356aab9cd1a24587ea0bcbfd33dcdaf0c51944a7","tid":1847421,"uid":3890